# Implementation Plan - Standalone Premium Music Platform

Build a completely new, standalone, production-ready music platform in the `music_player website` directory. This will be a high-performance Next.js application featuring glassmorphism, neon aesthetics, and advanced animations.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Project Initialization**: I will initialize a new Next.js project using `create-next-app` with TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and App Router.
> **GSAP Installation**: I will install `gsap` for advanced animations.
> **Music API**: I will use the Jamendo API for high-quality, free music access without requiring authentication.
> **Local Storage**: I will implement persistent state for "Favorites" and "Recently Played" using browser's LocalStorage.

